Mother is one being on this earth

00:00:04.166 --> 00:00:07.083
who can actually give that Self-realization,

00:00:07.333 --> 00:00:10.166
who can actually give you that enlightenment.

00:00:10.417 --> 00:00:13.333
No sitting in little rooms doing

00:00:13.542 --> 00:00:16.792
strange positions for months on end,

00:00:17.083 --> 00:00:20.542
to purify yourself and get yourself to some higher plain,

00:00:20.750 --> 00:00:24.583
no sitting down, repeating mantras endlessly on the hope that

00:00:24.834 --> 00:00:29.041
maybe one day you will reach some other state of consciousness,

00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:32.959
or some other higher stage of development, evolution.

00:00:33.125 --> 00:00:38.834
Mataji can give you that realization this evening.

00:00:39.333 --> 00:00:43.583
The only prerequisite is the desire for it

00:00:43.792 --> 00:00:48.458
and humility within yourself to be able to ask Her for it.

00:00:49.458 --> 00:00:54.959
I'll explain a little bit about this picture.

00:00:55.166 --> 00:01:00.333
As you'll see there are one, two, three, four, five, six, seven

00:01:00.667 --> 00:01:05.667
different major centers marked in the diagram.

00:01:05.999 --> 00:01:11.750
They represent what we call chakras,

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:17.999
which are energy centers within the spinal column.

00:01:18.333 --> 00:01:20.583
Now they are not things that you can carve open a spine

00:01:20.834 --> 00:01:22.583
and see within them, they are

00:01:22.834 --> 00:01:24.667
subtle energy centers, in the same way

00:01:24.917 --> 00:01:27.999
that you can't pull a television set apart and see the picture.

00:01:28.166 --> 00:01:34.083
They're there, they exist, they affect our behaviour,

00:01:34.417 --> 00:01:38.166
our behaviour affects them, too, just as importantly.

00:01:39.333 --> 00:01:45.333
They have been with us all the time, they are part of our absolute,

00:01:47.083 --> 00:01:51.834
inner structure, they are part of our absolute being.

00:01:52.333 --> 00:01:57.125
When a person is in the presence

00:01:57.333 --> 00:02:00.667
of a realized soul,

00:02:00.917 --> 00:02:05.834
such as Mataji Nirmala Devi, a process can occur,

00:02:06.083 --> 00:02:11.208
whereby the Kundalini, which is, if you like it's that

00:02:11.417 --> 00:02:14.999
tiny first energy that is created,

00:02:15.166 --> 00:02:18.417
and is placed within each living entity.

00:02:18.667 --> 00:02:20.667
And the Kundalini resides,

00:02:20.917 --> 00:02:25.625
in that triangiular area there, which is in us, the sacrum,

00:02:25.834 --> 00:02:29.625
the coccyx, that bone right at the bottom of the spine,

00:02:29.834 --> 00:02:32.333
that is where that energy resides.

00:02:32.583 --> 00:02:37.166
I don't know if you are aware of it, but

00:02:38.083 --> 00:02:40.834
the actual word itself, sacrum,

00:02:41.083 --> 00:02:45.750
means, is from the same root structure as the word sacred,

00:02:45.999 --> 00:02:49.625
it's I mean, the very fact that that is the word we call it,

00:02:49.834 --> 00:02:51.917
means that somewhere back in our

00:02:52.166 --> 00:02:53.417
in our history, we knew

00:02:53.667 --> 00:02:57.333
that there was something very special about that particular bone.

00:02:58.166 --> 00:03:02.041
The Kundalini energy resides in there and

00:03:02.250 --> 00:03:06.166
another thing about that bone is, if a person say is burned,

00:03:06.417 --> 00:03:10.000
that is the bone that remains right until the last,

00:03:10.250 --> 00:03:12.500
it's the last bone to burn.

00:03:12.750 --> 00:03:16.500
It's just a quality about it, that it's very special.

00:03:16.750 --> 00:03:18.542
The Kundalini resides there

00:03:18.750 --> 00:03:22.583
and that is the energy which when awakened

00:03:22.959 --> 00:03:26.834
travels up through the different centers,

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:31.125
all the way up through the spinal column itself and

00:03:31.333 --> 00:03:34.625
eventually when what we call enlightenment occurs,

00:03:34.834 --> 00:03:39.834
that energy actually comes out through the top of our heads.

00:03:40.083 --> 00:03:44.083
It might sound a little strange but you can feel that energy,

00:03:44.333 --> 00:03:48.750
and hopefully you'll all be able to feel it this evening.

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:52.166
And you can feel it as a cool breeze.

00:03:52.417 --> 00:03:53.458
Now, you know,

00:03:53.667 --> 00:03:56.999
some people actually feel it like there's a little fan sitting

00:03:57.166 --> 00:04:00.166
on top of their head blowing a little jet of cool air out there.

00:04:00.417 --> 00:04:01.750
It happens.

00:04:01.999 --> 00:04:04.250
You can't explain it in physical terms,

00:04:04.500 --> 00:04:08.250
it's an actual event, it actually occurs.

00:04:08.500 --> 00:04:12.750
You can also feel this coolness across your palms.

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:18.999
You may have heard of the breath of the Holy Spirit.

00:04:19.250 --> 00:04:21.458
That is what the cool breeze is.

00:04:21.667 --> 00:04:24.291
The Indians have a word for it,

00:04:24.500 --> 00:04:29.417
called 'chaitanya', which again is a cool breeze.

00:04:29.750 --> 00:04:34.750
The Middle Eastern people have a word for it, it's called the 'ruh',

00:04:34.999 --> 00:04:36.458
it is the cool breeze.

00:04:36.667 --> 00:04:40.500
It's a thing that unfortunately we in the West

00:04:40.750 --> 00:04:42.500
haven't heard all that much about

00:04:42.750 --> 00:04:45.125
because our pursuits over the last

00:04:45.333 --> 00:04:49.583
couple of thousands years have been basically material,

00:04:49.834 --> 00:04:53.583
whereas in a lot of other cultures, in a lot of other countries,

00:04:53.834 --> 00:04:56.500
the thing behind people's lives

00:04:56.750 --> 00:05:00.999
isn't what material things they may own or may aquire or

00:05:01.166 --> 00:05:04.208
what intellectual pursuits they may follow. It is

00:05:04.417 --> 00:05:08.999
whether or not they are or can be connected with that

00:05:09.166 --> 00:05:13.750
primordial energy and that total energy which some people call God,

00:05:13.999 --> 00:05:18.083
some people call the Spirit, whatever name you want to call it.

00:05:18.333 --> 00:05:21.750
Some cultures in the world are for years being trying to get

00:05:21.999 --> 00:05:25.834
themselves aligned with that Spirit, aligned with that energy.

00:05:26.166 --> 00:05:29.999
We in the West have steered ourselves way away from there.

00:05:30.250 --> 00:05:34.000
However, obviously, there's plenty of people here,

00:05:34.250 --> 00:05:37.834
who want to know a little more about it and want if they can to be

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:42.834
reconnected, cause it's what we all came for in the first place,

00:05:43.166 --> 00:05:44.834
with that energy.

00:05:45.083 --> 00:05:47.333
Now the way that Kundalini works

00:05:47.583 --> 00:05:50.583
is that first,

00:05:50.834 --> 00:05:54.583
it has to be awakened by

00:05:54.834 --> 00:05:57.834
the energies first in that,

00:05:58.083 --> 00:06:01.500
a little red four petaled chakra,

00:06:01.750 --> 00:06:06.834
at the base there; it gives permission to the Kundalini or gives,

00:06:07.083 --> 00:06:09.083
gives notice to the Kundalini, that

00:06:09.333 --> 00:06:12.999
now is the time for it to be awakened.

00:06:13.583 --> 00:06:17.750
It stirs and passes up through...

00:06:17.999 --> 00:06:20.999
The first chakra by the way, is called the Mooladhara chakra.

00:06:21.166 --> 00:06:25.709
Mooladhara means the root,

00:06:25.917 --> 00:06:27.834
the support of the root,

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:31.417
all right? It's the actual thing that holds it, all

00:06:31.667 --> 00:06:36.417
the whole thing rests on, the whole thing has to grow out from.

00:06:38.417 --> 00:06:40.500
I'll explain right from the beginning too,

00:06:40.750 --> 00:06:44.583
that another thing that occurs as the Kundalini awakens is

00:06:44.834 --> 00:06:48.750
you can actually, if you have a problem within yourself you can

00:06:48.999 --> 00:06:50.999
find out where it is and do something about it

00:06:51.166 --> 00:06:54.834
because as you can see the colours correspond with colours

00:06:55.083 --> 00:06:56.667
we have drawn on the hands.

