We've since learned out how to correct it but we haven't quite

00:07:15.083 --> 00:07:17.542
finished doing it at the moment. However you get

00:07:17.750 --> 00:07:21.333
the correspondance from the colours and as you can see this spot

00:07:21.583 --> 00:07:26.750
here, on the hand, is the same colour as that spot at the base

00:07:26.999 --> 00:07:31.417
of the spine which is the Mooladhara and if you hold your hands out,

00:07:31.667 --> 00:07:37.083
to Mataji for instance, you may feel a numbness or a tingling

00:07:37.333 --> 00:07:40.750
or something in the base of your palm,

00:07:40.999 --> 00:07:45.834
which means that there is some problem in that particular chakra

00:07:46.166 --> 00:07:50.542
within your own subtle body and you can, if you have some problem,

00:07:50.750 --> 00:07:54.834
you can proceed to do something about it and get rid of them.

00:07:55.083 --> 00:07:58.125
The Kundalini does the work for you. It gets rid of the problems.

00:07:58.333 --> 00:08:02.041
You just have to have it awakened and it starts to take care of you.

00:08:02.250 --> 00:08:04.834
It is as it were your own mother,

00:08:05.083 --> 00:08:08.834
it has loved you since the beginning of creation and we'll take,

00:08:09.083 --> 00:08:12.750
you know, now that you have the chance for it to be awakened within you

00:08:12.999 --> 00:08:17.166
it will, it will quite, you will notice,

00:08:17.417 --> 00:08:19.999
right from the beginning that it will start to look after you,

00:08:20.166 --> 00:08:23.417
that there is this energy there that can take care of you on

00:08:23.667 --> 00:08:25.750
many, many, many levels.

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:29.417
The Kundalini energy awakens, from the Mooladhara

00:08:29.667 --> 00:08:35.542
it goes up to that green center in the middle there first,

00:08:35.750 --> 00:08:38.083
which we call the Nabhi chakra.

00:08:38.333 --> 00:08:41.291
Nabhi means navel. It is the chakra that is

00:08:41.500 --> 00:08:45.500
behind the navel in the body. It has to do with...

00:08:45.750 --> 00:08:49.458
They, they all have different qualities, all the chakras. This,

00:08:49.667 --> 00:08:52.500
the particular quality of the Nabhi chakra is

00:08:52.750 --> 00:08:55.500
to do with our sustenance, to do with our,

00:08:55.750 --> 00:09:01.417
what we could call our dharma, the way we live.

00:09:01.667 --> 00:09:06.834
I mean it's, say for instance, a man drinks very heavily,

00:09:07.083 --> 00:09:11.999
gambles a lot, goes out with a lot of different women,

00:09:13.417 --> 00:09:18.250
indulges in different drugs perhaps. Any, any of those things,

00:09:18.500 --> 00:09:20.166
they are not things that are going to destroy you

00:09:20.417 --> 00:09:24.500
but they are things that they are going to make it harder for you to

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:28.000
live a balanced life within yourself.

00:09:28.834 --> 00:09:31.750
And that has to do with this center here, with the Nabhi,

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.625
with the dharma of the person.

00:09:33.834 --> 00:09:36.291
As the Kundalini awakens, it goes to that center and

00:09:36.625 --> 00:09:41.291
as it gets enlightened, those qualities of dharma -

00:09:41.500 --> 00:09:44.375
the Indian word "dharma", we can call it right living,

00:09:44.583 --> 00:09:48.250
I think we might have heard of that term - whatever term we use,

00:09:48.500 --> 00:09:50.667
that is the quality that comes from there

00:09:50.917 --> 00:09:54.166
and as the Kundalini passes through there and awakens that center,

00:09:54.417 --> 00:09:57.291
those qualities can start to come out in our own life.

00:09:57.500 --> 00:10:00.625
Then it drops back down to the orange coloured

00:10:00.834 --> 00:10:04.250
center there which we call the Swadhisthan.

00:10:04.583 --> 00:10:06.834
It has to do with creativity ...

00:10:07.083 --> 00:10:11.750
as an artistic activity,

00:10:11.999 --> 00:10:16.999
and it also as you can see is the beginning of that yellow line,

00:10:17.166 --> 00:10:21.750
all right?  Now that yellow line is one we use to denote

00:10:22.083 --> 00:10:26.667
what is called the right hand sympathetic nervous system. All right?

00:10:26.917 --> 00:10:30.000
Now we all have heard about the sympathetic nervous system.

00:10:30.250 --> 00:10:33.041
We have, on the diagram there, you'll see the yellow line,

00:10:33.250 --> 00:10:35.750
the white line and the blue line. The yellow line,

00:10:35.999 --> 00:10:39.333
is the right side sympathetic nervous system. It has to do with

00:10:39.583 --> 00:10:45.417
activity, with the future, with planning, with

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:50.333
the ego eventually. As you can see it passes all the way through,

00:10:50.583 --> 00:10:54.834
right up until it actually crosses over this center here,

00:10:55.083 --> 00:10:58.750
and ends up on this section of the head here,

00:10:59.000 --> 00:11:01.583
which is where what

00:11:01.834 --> 00:11:05.250
we call ego resides.

00:11:05.583 --> 00:11:08.834
It's a thing we've all got, it's a thing that's been necessary

00:11:09.166 --> 00:11:11.999
to us to have, to get to the stage of development

00:11:12.166 --> 00:11:14.458
that we have reached, internally.

00:11:14.667 --> 00:11:18.166
I mean we have been involved in a growth process,

00:11:18.417 --> 00:11:20.542
in a, in an evolutionary process,

00:11:20.750 --> 00:11:24.083
that's finally brought us to the stage we are now:

00:11:24.583 --> 00:11:26.583
Mental capacities have grown,

00:11:26.834 --> 00:11:29.375
we have our physical capacities evolved,

00:11:29.583 --> 00:11:32.417
you know, we slowly evolved to the point we are now.

00:11:32.667 --> 00:11:36.542
We are at the purple coloured center there which we call

00:11:36.750 --> 00:11:41.750
the Sahasrar, which is when the human being

00:11:41.999 --> 00:11:44.166
is evolved that stage,

00:11:44.500 --> 00:11:47.125
it is possible for that chakra to be opened.

00:11:47.333 --> 00:11:48.834
And it is at that point

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:53.417
that the connection with the All Pervading occurs, with

00:11:53.667 --> 00:11:57.500
the Divine, the connection with the Divine occurs.

00:11:57.917 --> 00:12:01.333
It happens at that center and to get there we have to

00:12:01.583 --> 00:12:04.250
go all the way through all of the chakras, right?

00:12:04.500 --> 00:12:08.834
So we go from the Swadisthan, the active principle there,

00:12:09.000 --> 00:12:12.291
the creative side, and from the Swadhisthan,

00:12:12.500 --> 00:12:16.834
we pass across that large green area, which is the Void,

00:12:17.083 --> 00:12:19.500
we could call it the ocean of illusion,

00:12:19.750 --> 00:12:22.417
if you like. It's all of the things that are around us all the time,

00:12:22.667 --> 00:12:23.667
and trying to distract us,

00:12:23.917 --> 00:12:27.291
all the things that are taking our attention away from

00:12:27.500 --> 00:12:30.041
what we really are, what we are really seeking,

00:12:30.250 --> 00:12:34.083
all of those things. And as we evolve, as we sort of discard,

00:12:34.333 --> 00:12:38.250
all of the different divertions, you know, you may follow one path

00:12:38.500 --> 00:12:40.999
for years and years and years and finally after

00:12:41.166 --> 00:12:43.583
getting an extremly bitter taste in your mouth, eventually

00:12:43.834 --> 00:12:45.750
you think, "All right. I've had enough of that one.

00:12:45.999 --> 00:12:47.625
It hasn't reached me what I wanted,

00:12:47.834 --> 00:12:49.834
I'm going to try something else".

00:12:50.083 --> 00:12:53.291
Now we do that not just for one or two years

00:12:53.500 --> 00:12:56.750
but we do that for lifetime, after lifetime, after lifetime,

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:59.667
to the point where we finally sort ourselves out

00:12:59.999 --> 00:13:04.417
and to the point where we finally get to where you are now

00:13:04.667 --> 00:13:08.417
which is coming to a meeting hopefully

00:13:08.667 --> 00:13:11.250
to find something out about Kundalini hopefully,

00:13:11.500 --> 00:13:14.999
to gain enlightenment, which is the thing that we are all seeking,

00:13:15.166 --> 00:13:16.583
it's the thing we have all -

00:13:16.834 --> 00:13:19.917
that has been driving us right from the beginning of creation

00:13:20.083 --> 00:13:21.750
that's what it´s about, you know.

