and that that love is what is behind absolutely everything,

00:15:42.583 --> 00:15:46.083
absolutely it is the, it is the thing out of

00:15:46.333 --> 00:15:50.834
which the whole of creation has grown, is that love, and we all have

00:15:51.083 --> 00:15:54.333
a tiny bit of that within us,

00:15:54.583 --> 00:15:58.750
actually it resides in our heart.

00:15:59.625 --> 00:16:03.000
If the heart stops, the life stops. It's where it is.

00:16:03.250 --> 00:16:09.000
Now what happens, is as the Kundalini rises it awakens that center

00:16:09.250 --> 00:16:12.917
again we have the next center, the Vishuddhi chakra.

