00:16:52.667 --> 00:16:56.458
to actually it's the break from being an animal to being a human

00:16:56.667 --> 00:16:59.291
occurs at that point. And it is that point

00:16:59.500 --> 00:17:03.917
that we start to communicate where we have words, where we have

00:17:04.166 --> 00:17:07.125
gestures, where we have facial expressions,

00:17:07.333 --> 00:17:11.125
all of those things actually start to operate from this chakra here,

00:17:11.333 --> 00:17:13.166
the Vishuddhi chakra.

00:17:13.417 --> 00:17:15.417
And the Kundalini passes through there,

00:17:15.709 --> 00:17:18.583
and to the - what's called the Agnya chakra.

00:17:18.834 --> 00:17:22.166
Some people might call it the 'third eye'.

00:17:22.417 --> 00:17:25.667
It is a third eye in a sense but it's an inward looking eye,

00:17:25.917 --> 00:17:30.500
that's not one that you look out through.

00:17:30.750 --> 00:17:33.583
It is where Jesus Christ resides.

00:17:33.834 --> 00:17:38.500
When we have the words of Christ,

00:17:38.834 --> 00:17:42.834
that "You must pass through Me to get to My Father",

00:17:43.083 --> 00:17:46.083
that is precisely what He is talking about.

00:17:46.333 --> 00:17:48.667
You have to pass through that center.

00:17:48.917 --> 00:17:51.417
You have to get as it were the "o.k."

00:17:51.667 --> 00:17:56.542
from Jesus that you may pass, that the Kundalini energy may pass

00:17:56.750 --> 00:18:01.000
through there and may pass into the Sahasrara, where,

00:18:01.250 --> 00:18:07.166
this center, the crown, will open and connect you

00:18:08.250 --> 00:18:10.834
with the Divine.

00:18:11.166 --> 00:18:14.500
The quality of that chakra,

00:18:14.792 --> 00:18:19.750
one we tend to forget in the so-called christian countries,

00:18:19.999 --> 00:18:22.500
is the quality of forgiveness.

00:18:22.750 --> 00:18:25.834
I don't think we can have any greater lesson

00:18:26.083 --> 00:18:30.333
than that of Jesus, the Lord Himself,

00:18:30.583 --> 00:18:33.250
as He was being crucified, saying,

00:18:33.500 --> 00:18:35.999
"Forgive them, Father, for they know not what they do".

00:18:36.166 --> 00:18:41.417
I mean, there He was, was the most powerful being in creation

00:18:41.709 --> 00:18:44.834
who could have.. who could have destroyed

00:18:45.083 --> 00:18:48.667
everyone and everything. He was there,

00:18:48.999 --> 00:18:54.500
begging His Father that His murderers be forgiven,

00:18:54.792 --> 00:18:58.667
and it's an incredible thing, it's, you know, I mean, a human being

00:18:58.999 --> 00:19:04.291
can only ever aspire to that wisdom and to that absolute love,

00:19:04.500 --> 00:19:07.999
cause that's what it came from when He said that.

00:19:08.250 --> 00:19:14.000
And that is the quality of the Agnya chakra.

00:19:14.291 --> 00:19:16.417
People may find,

00:19:16.667 --> 00:19:20.834
they get headaches a lot, that they worry a lot,

00:19:21.000 --> 00:19:22.999
that there's a whole lot of mental activity.

00:19:23.250 --> 00:19:26.083
Anything to do with this center here,

00:19:26.333 --> 00:19:31.999
tends to pass, if somewhere within yourself you can find out

00:19:32.250 --> 00:19:34.583
who it is that you haven't forgiven.

00:19:34.834 --> 00:19:36.041
Might be yourself, you know,

00:19:36.250 --> 00:19:37.999
you might be incredibly hard on yourself.

00:19:38.166 --> 00:19:40.667
One of the hardest things to do is to forgive yourself,

00:19:40.999 --> 00:19:43.750
for all of the things that you feel you may or may not have done.

00:19:43.999 --> 00:19:48.417
Is to turn around and say, "o.k., you are forgiven" , you know ...

00:19:48.667 --> 00:19:52.500
end of it. And as that quality of forgiveness starts

00:19:52.750 --> 00:19:56.750
to come into our own lives, the Agnya chakra itself,

00:19:56.999 --> 00:20:01.500
begins to work more fully and to give its blessings to us.

00:20:01.834 --> 00:20:07.000
At the Sahasrar, what is called the thousand petalled lotus

00:20:07.250 --> 00:20:12.083
in Indian religious teaching,

00:20:12.333 --> 00:20:16.750
is where all of the qualities of all of the chakras

00:20:16.999 --> 00:20:21.834
are merged into one, and our balance starts.

00:20:22.083 --> 00:20:25.333
There actually,

00:20:26.999 --> 00:20:30.250
each particular center as it were, has its seats

00:20:30.500 --> 00:20:33.834
on the actual head itself

00:20:34.083 --> 00:20:38.583
and they all move up to actually like,

00:20:38.834 --> 00:20:41.083
not like the United Nations but

00:20:41.333 --> 00:20:43.999
they all converge in the one area

00:20:44.166 --> 00:20:46.999
and can govern your life from there,

00:20:47.166 --> 00:20:51.000
with peace and freedom.

00:20:52.750 --> 00:20:58.250
You'll see, I've spoken about the yellow side, the right hand side -

00:20:58.500 --> 00:21:03.834
ah, here is Mother, Mother, Mataji now. She will speak with us.

00:21:10.834 --> 00:21:14.166
So go ahead. I'll speak after.

00:21:15.750 --> 00:21:20.417
I was just about to speak about the left hand side.

00:21:24.750 --> 00:21:27.250
It is the side of the past,

00:21:27.500 --> 00:21:32.166
of our memories, of our conditioning,

00:21:32.417 --> 00:21:35.500
of why we look back at all the things that we used to do and

00:21:35.750 --> 00:21:39.417
think about why can't we be like that now, all of those things.

00:21:39.667 --> 00:21:44.166
They are things, qualities, on the left hand side.

00:21:44.417 --> 00:21:48.500
Now, we can dissapear right out in the left hand side,

00:21:48.750 --> 00:21:51.208
into what's called the subconscious,

00:21:51.417 --> 00:21:53.458
into what's called the collective subconscious.

00:21:53.667 --> 00:21:55.375
We are not only dealing with our past,

00:21:55.583 --> 00:21:58.667
we are dealing with the past of many, many, many people.

00:21:58.875 --> 00:22:01.333
And we can get very lost in that area.

00:22:01.583 --> 00:22:04.125
In the same way that when we go too far on the other side,

00:22:04.333 --> 00:22:06.667
on the right hand side, into the future.

00:22:06.917 --> 00:22:11.166
We get into the areas where again we lose control,

00:22:11.417 --> 00:22:13.583
where we, we don't know who we are,

00:22:13.834 --> 00:22:18.750
where we get joined in with all of the egos and all of the futures

00:22:18.999 --> 00:22:23.166
of many, many, many other people, aside from ourselves, and we can

00:22:23.417 --> 00:22:26.166
what we call the supraconscious, the collective supraconscious,

00:22:26.417 --> 00:22:29.083
we can get lost into that area also.

00:22:29.333 --> 00:22:30.083
However,

00:22:30.333 --> 00:22:33.500
as you can see there is that pure line up through the center,

00:22:33.750 --> 00:22:35.458
which is the central nervous system,

00:22:35.667 --> 00:22:37.458
the parasympathetic nervous system,

00:22:37.667 --> 00:22:41.041
which is where the Kundalini will pass,

00:22:41.250 --> 00:22:44.750
and where that energy can bring us back towards the center,

00:22:44.959 --> 00:22:47.083
bring us back towards the point,

00:22:47.333 --> 00:22:49.750
where finally it will pass through all the chakras

00:22:49.999 --> 00:22:52.834
and through the Sahasrar, giving us enlightenment

00:22:53.083 --> 00:22:55.166
and giving us the union with the Divine,

00:22:55.417 --> 00:22:59.166
which is what we are seeking, Mother.

00:23:07.875 --> 00:23:11.500
Ladies and gentlemen, I have great pleasure in introducing to you,

00:23:11.750 --> 00:23:16.542
Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi. She has come to Melbourne,

00:23:16.750 --> 00:23:19.917
and I think probably the most important thing that,

00:23:20.166 --> 00:23:22.750
at a material level that She's managed to bring for all of us

00:23:22.999 --> 00:23:25.333
is this beautiful rain.

00:23:25.625 --> 00:23:28.083
As She drove in from the airport today,

00:23:28.333 --> 00:23:31.000
somebody said to Her: "Mother we need rain", so

00:23:31.250 --> 00:23:33.166
She just put Her attention to it and

00:23:33.417 --> 00:23:35.583
the heaven seemed to have opened tonight.

00:23:35.875 --> 00:23:37.500
But at the much more subtle level,

00:23:37.750 --> 00:23:40.667
She's able to give us far more as Bill has been saying,

00:23:40.999 --> 00:23:44.250
She's able to give us the experience of Self-realization.

00:23:44.500 --> 00:23:47.333
We've come to that point in our evolution where we have to

00:23:47.583 --> 00:23:52.917
make that final ascent and become a higher being,

00:23:53.291 --> 00:23:57.542
a being which becomes one with God,

00:23:57.750 --> 00:24:01.166
a being which becomes a subtler being, which

00:24:01.417 --> 00:24:04.166
not only responds to those things,

00:24:04.417 --> 00:24:07.834
which we traditionally call our ego

00:24:08.125 --> 00:24:10.583
or our superego, which is really our subconscious,

00:24:10.834 --> 00:24:14.333
but we respond to the nature of the Spirit, which is eternal,

00:24:14.583 --> 00:24:16.750
but which is sleeping within us.

00:24:17.000 --> 00:24:18.500
After Self-realization,

00:24:18.834 --> 00:24:24.750
this energy of Kundalini rises and with the Spirit,

00:24:25.125 --> 00:24:29.000
puts you in touch with the all pervading Spirit of God.

00:24:29.333 --> 00:24:32.333
And at that moment when, it passes through the Sahasrar,

00:24:32.583 --> 00:24:36.917
this chakra at the top of the head, you become one with God.

00:24:37.083 --> 00:24:39.750
You become a realized soul, you become a "pir",

00:24:39.999 --> 00:24:43.667
as it refers to in the Muslim scriptures.

00:24:43.959 --> 00:24:48.000
You become [pa] as it's said in the Hindu scriptures.

00:24:48.417 --> 00:24:52.750
It's there and it happens, it's an experience.

00:24:53.083 --> 00:24:56.291
And yet, one might ask why is it so easy and how do

00:24:56.500 --> 00:24:58.999
such a large number of people get it.

00:24:59.250 --> 00:25:03.250
I've seen six thousand people get it in a meeting in India.

00:25:03.542 --> 00:25:06.208
There are very few people here tonight but at some of the meetings,

00:25:06.417 --> 00:25:08.834
which Shri Mataji conducts,

00:25:09.083 --> 00:25:13.166
even in recently last night and the night before in Adelaide,

00:25:13.417 --> 00:25:18.500
three and four hundred at a time get their Self-realization.

00:25:19.083 --> 00:25:23.999
It happens enmass because the grace of God is overflowing now.

00:25:24.250 --> 00:25:28.000
And here on the earth is somebody who gives an enlightened light,

00:25:28.250 --> 00:25:32.417
who can give it freely, to everyone.

00:25:32.667 --> 00:25:35.834
Just in Her presence the Kundalini awakens,

00:25:36.083 --> 00:25:39.250
just by merely stretching your hands out towards Her.

00:25:39.542 --> 00:25:45.083
That subtlety that lies within you is awakened and all your seeking,

00:25:45.333 --> 00:25:50.417
over your many, many lives is rewarded at this moment.

00:25:50.709 --> 00:25:56.417
You've been drawn here in a very, very, extraordinary way.

00:25:56.667 --> 00:26:01.333
It's no accident that all of you are here tonight.

00:26:01.625 --> 00:26:04.834
It's the reward of your seeking as I said. So,

00:26:05.083 --> 00:26:07.417
in a very humble way, but

00:26:07.625 --> 00:26:09.625
remaining scientific to the extent

00:26:09.834 --> 00:26:12.166
that you keep an open mind about it,

00:26:12.417 --> 00:26:14.250
I suggest that

00:26:14.500 --> 00:26:18.667
you listen to what Mataji has to say but more than that you,

00:26:18.999 --> 00:26:22.125
allow yourself to experience the cool vibrations,

00:26:22.333 --> 00:26:24.417
that were refer to in the Christian scriptures

00:26:24.667 --> 00:26:26.834
as the cool wind of the Holy Spirit,

00:26:27.000 --> 00:26:31.458
which Mohammed said would be flowing in the hands.

00:26:31.667 --> 00:26:37.834
In fact he said, at this time of resurection, your hands will speak.

00:26:38.667 --> 00:26:42.250
The Hindu scriptures, many, many of them have said it,

00:26:42.500 --> 00:26:48.875
Adi Shankaracharya in the sixth century, spoke very, very eloquently

00:26:49.041 --> 00:26:53.333
about the chaitanya, which again is this cool vibrations,

00:26:53.583 --> 00:26:55.041
which we feel on the hands,

00:26:55.250 --> 00:26:57.834
and which we feel coming from the top of the head.

00:26:58.125 --> 00:27:02.083
So as Bill has explained the subtle centers within us,

00:27:02.333 --> 00:27:03.750
as he's explained the left side and

00:27:03.999 --> 00:27:05.999
the right side of our subtle body,

00:27:06.166 --> 00:27:10.083
in other words as he's explained the mechanism that lies within,

00:27:10.333 --> 00:27:14.250
now, really all that has to happen is, you have to get it.

00:27:14.500 --> 00:27:17.834
And as you get it, you can give it to others.

00:27:18.125 --> 00:27:22.500
This is the great joy of Self-realization,

00:27:22.917 --> 00:27:25.250
since the advent of Shri Mataji.

00:27:25.583 --> 00:27:30.333
So when you get it, you should develop it,

00:27:30.583 --> 00:27:33.917
when you develop it you'll find that all your physical and emotional

00:27:34.083 --> 00:27:38.333
and mental problems will dissolve. But that's only a by-product.

00:27:38.625 --> 00:27:41.583
And then of course you have to give it to others.

00:27:41.959 --> 00:27:45.125
Because as you get the blessings of God, so too,

00:27:45.333 --> 00:27:47.834
those blessings must be given to others.

00:27:48.083 --> 00:27:52.750
Sahaja Yoga is not a club, it's not a cult, it's not an organization

00:27:52.999 --> 00:27:55.583
and you certainly you can't pay any money for it.

00:27:55.959 --> 00:27:56.792
And yet,

00:27:56.999 --> 00:28:02.166
quietly but very encouragingly it is growing throughout the world.

00:28:02.417 --> 00:28:05.291
I have just arrived in Australia with Shri Mataji

00:28:05.500 --> 00:28:09.000
as part of a world tour that She is conducting this year,

00:28:09.250 --> 00:28:12.750
throughout England, the whole of Europe, South East Asia.

00:28:12.999 --> 00:28:16.834
She's been through India along with about sixty of us,

00:28:17.125 --> 00:28:22.750
us - meaning the Australians, English, French, German, Italian,

00:28:22.999 --> 00:28:27.333
American, Canadian, all sort of nations have been

00:28:27.583 --> 00:28:30.667
with Her watching the miracle of Sahaja Yoga, spreading

00:28:30.917 --> 00:28:34.458
throughout India. But we are watching its spread towards the West,

00:28:34.667 --> 00:28:36.500
and it's catching on like wild fire.

00:28:36.792 --> 00:28:40.500
Catching on meaning, people are getting their Self-realization and

00:28:40.792 --> 00:28:44.083
developing it, and becoming complete beings,

00:28:44.291 --> 00:28:49.083
getting their inner satisfaction, their inner joy,

00:28:49.417 --> 00:28:51.375
and knowing that they reached the goal

00:28:51.583 --> 00:28:54.250
that they've been seeking over their many lives.

00:28:54.500 --> 00:29:00.250
Mataji is the wife of an eminent diplomat,

00:29:00.458 --> 00:29:04.000
he's the Secretary General of the United Nations Organizations,

00:29:04.250 --> 00:29:09.999
United Nations Organization, International Maritime Organization.

00:29:10.250 --> 00:29:15.917
She's a housewife, She's a mother, She's a grandmother.

00:29:16.250 --> 00:29:20.625
She's well-known as the daughter of the Salve family in India,

00:29:20.834 --> 00:29:24.417
who were freedom fighters of the time of Gandhi

00:29:24.709 --> 00:29:28.667
and that period when the British rule came to an end.

00:29:28.999 --> 00:29:30.667
She's the sister of the Cabinet Minister

00:29:30.917 --> 00:29:33.999
in the Indira Gandhi government.

00:29:34.166 --> 00:29:38.166
So She's very well-known at the international level but

00:29:38.417 --> 00:29:40.583
that level She plays down,

00:29:40.834 --> 00:29:44.333
that level She's not really so interested in.

00:29:44.542 --> 00:29:47.667
That which She is interested in is the Spirit.

00:29:47.999 --> 00:29:53.583
In Her very warm, in Her very loving, in Her very tender way,

00:29:53.875 --> 00:29:59.750
Her devotees, those people who gained their Self-realization,

00:30:00.250 --> 00:30:04.375
are those to whom She devotes Her greatest attention.

00:30:04.583 --> 00:30:10.000
So, whether you know Her in person, in the physical sense,

00:30:10.291 --> 00:30:14.333
or whether you gain your Self-realization even from Her photograph,

00:30:14.625 --> 00:30:19.583
doesn't matter. Her blessings pour towards you

00:30:19.792 --> 00:30:22.458
and through you, and slowly you start

00:30:22.667 --> 00:30:26.583
to feel that bliss and that joy that have been spoken of

00:30:26.834 --> 00:30:30.417
so eloquently and so widely in all the scriptures.

00:30:30.667 --> 00:30:32.709
It sounds too good to be true.

00:30:32.917 --> 00:30:35.500
I must admit it sounds too good to be true.

00:30:35.750 --> 00:30:39.083
So again I say, be open minded,

00:30:39.333 --> 00:30:43.750
even be scientific, keep it as a hypothesis at first.

00:30:44.000 --> 00:30:45.667
See that you feel the cool wind.

00:30:45.999 --> 00:30:47.583
Don't mistake it for the air conditioning.

00:30:47.834 --> 00:30:49.834
It's a quite different coefficient.

00:30:50.125 --> 00:30:55.917
You feel the cool vibrations over and through,

00:30:56.166 --> 00:31:00.250
and almost as if flowing through the body.

00:31:00.500 --> 00:31:03.417
You feel it in a very, very subtle way.

00:31:03.667 --> 00:31:05.750
Your ego will say, "Is it the wind that's blowing

00:31:05.999 --> 00:31:08.999
from the air conditioner?" It's not like that at all.

00:31:09.208 --> 00:31:11.458
We've been in rooms which have been absolutely

00:31:11.667 --> 00:31:13.250
without air conditioning.

00:31:13.500 --> 00:31:16.583
We've been in halls like this which are completely sealed.

00:31:16.834 --> 00:31:18.083
It makes no difference.

00:31:18.333 --> 00:31:20.999
But you have to feel those cool vibrations.

00:31:21.166 --> 00:31:23.667
But if you don't feel it, don't be too dissapointed,

00:31:23.959 --> 00:31:29.000
because Shri Mataji will probably work on the centers a little,

00:31:29.333 --> 00:31:31.667
help to clear the centers a little,

00:31:31.999 --> 00:31:34.583
explain to you what might be the problem,

00:31:34.834 --> 00:31:39.750
and generally assist you, in the experience of Self-realization.

00:31:39.999 --> 00:31:42.500
So without any further introduction from me,

00:31:42.750 --> 00:31:46.417
it gives me great pleasure to again introduce to you, in Melbourne,

00:31:46.625 --> 00:31:50.417
Her Holiness Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi.

00:32:07.625 --> 00:32:12.750
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:17.667
We have to understand

00:32:17.917 --> 00:32:23.834
that God has created us as human beings with a purpose.

00:32:24.333 --> 00:32:27.000
But in those modern times,

00:32:27.250 --> 00:32:29.333
when we don’t even believe in God,

00:32:29.583 --> 00:32:34.250
or on a, in a Creator, or any such energy that exists,

00:32:34.500 --> 00:32:36.625
it’s very hard to talk of God

00:32:36.834 --> 00:32:38.834
and to introduce

00:32:39.083 --> 00:32:43.583
Him to be the One who has made us human beings.

00:32:43.834 --> 00:32:47.250
But even Darwin

00:32:47.500 --> 00:32:50.834
said that if man has come so far

00:32:51.083 --> 00:32:56.417
he will have to go a little further to understand himself.

00:32:56.667 --> 00:32:59.083
I would suggest that

00:32:59.291 --> 00:33:02.417
one has to only understand one point,

00:33:02.667 --> 00:33:05.500
that whatever we have so far known

00:33:05.750 --> 00:33:09.583
has been the knowledge of the tree.

00:33:09.917 --> 00:33:15.000
But we have to have the knowledge of the roots.

00:33:15.291 --> 00:33:17.750
To get the knowledge of the roots,

00:33:18.041 --> 00:33:21.583
we have to become subtler than what we are.

00:33:21.834 --> 00:33:26.750
This awareness, this human awareness, cannot take us that side.

00:33:26.999 --> 00:33:32.417
For example, you are all listening to Me very intensely,

00:33:32.667 --> 00:33:35.917
but if I say “Please take your attention inside”,

00:33:36.083 --> 00:33:38.083
you’ll say “How? Mother it’s impossible."

00:33:38.333 --> 00:33:41.083
'How do we take our attention inside?”

00:33:41.333 --> 00:33:44.834
It’s only possible when something happens within you

00:33:45.000 --> 00:33:49.000
that your attention is drawn inside,

00:33:49.250 --> 00:33:51.417
then only you will come to know

00:33:51.625 --> 00:33:57.083
that you are a beautiful instrument made through ages.

00:33:57.417 --> 00:34:02.166
All these centres that are shown here represent

00:34:02.375 --> 00:34:07.000
your evolutionary process, one by one, how you evolved,

00:34:07.250 --> 00:34:09.458
through ages

00:34:09.667 --> 00:34:14.667
to this stage of evolution.

00:34:14.875 --> 00:34:20.667
And now after evolving up to the human stage,

00:34:20.917 --> 00:34:23.500
what do we have to do?

